.TH CAST-DAEMON-FIXTURE 8 "2023-11-14" "cast-daemon-fixture @PROJECT_VERSION@"
.SH NAME
cast-daemon-fixture \- validate the generated daemon fixture configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cast-daemon-fixture
.BR --self-test
.br
.B cast-daemon-fixture
.BR --check-config " PATH"
.SH DESCRIPTION
Exercises a compiled daemon-like executable together with a generated default
configuration, systemd service unit, and administrator manual page.
